<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id449d8de2-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s1013"><num value="1013">§ 1013.</num><heading> Basis of property included in inventory</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">If the property should have been included in the last inventory, the basis shall be the last inventory value thereof.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id449d8de3-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a">(<ref href="/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736">Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/68A/296">68A Stat. 296</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
